<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今天的突破性故事|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com是您最新的中国新闻报道和时事的在线来源</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 21:13:55 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>特朗普说，他可能会在chagos群岛上接受英国的交易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/trump-says-he-is-likely-accept-uk-deal-chagos-islands-2025-02-27/</link><description>唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统周四表示，他倾向于支持英国与夏戈斯群岛（Chagos Islands）的美国英国军事基地的未来，以促进英国首相凯尔·斯塔默（Keir Starmer）的未来。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 19:51:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/trump-says-he-is-likely-accept-uk-deal-chagos-islands-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>官员说</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/mexico-analyzing-more-measures-crack-down-low-cost-shipments-official-says-2025-02-27/</link><description>一位官员周四表示，墨西哥正在权衡进一步的贸易措施，以打击低成本的货物，这是一位大部分来自中国的所谓“ de Minimis”购买后的关税。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 19:32:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/mexico-analyzing-more-measures-crack-down-low-cost-shipments-official-says-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>美国法院拒绝Hikvision竞标取消对设备批准的FCC禁令</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/us-court-rejects-hikvision-bid-lift-fcc-ban-equipment-approvals-2025-02-27/</link><description>美国上诉法院周四拒绝了Hikvision的竞标，要求取消联邦通信委员会对中国制造商生产的新视频监视和电信设备的批准。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 19:13:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/us-court-rejects-hikvision-bid-lift-fcc-ban-equipment-approvals-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>美国谴责泰国的40个Uyghurs返回中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-condemns-thailands-return-40-uyghurs-china-2025-02-27/</link><description>美国国务卿马可·卢比奥（Marco Rubio）周四谴责泰国至少40名乌耶（Uyghurs）返回中国，华盛顿说，穆斯林集团的成员面临种族灭绝。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 19:05:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-condemns-thailands-return-40-uyghurs-china-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>美国商务提名人说</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/report-tsmc-chips-made-huawei-huge-concern-us-commerce-nominee-says-2025-02-27/</link><description>美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的提名人周四负责监督出口政策，称台湾半导体制造业公司共同生产了成千上万的筹码，这些筹码进入了中国的华为，这是“巨大的关注”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 16:53:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/report-tsmc-chips-made-huawei-huge-concern-us-commerce-nominee-says-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>苹果提起手表的“碳中性”主张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-sued-over-carbon-neutral-claim-watches-2025-02-27/</link><description>苹果曾被消费者起诉，他们说其说明三种版本的苹果手表是“碳中性”的，环保友好的是虚假和误导性的。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 15:30:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-sued-over-carbon-neutral-claim-watches-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>COP30总裁说</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/china-plays-key-role-climate-change-may-be-looked-additional-leadership-cop30-2025-02-27/</link><description>COP30主席安德烈·阿兰哈·科雷亚·洛戈（Andre Aranha Correa do Lago Lago）周四表示，中国在应对气候变化方面起着非常重要的作用，其他人可能会寻求亚洲国家的额外领导地位。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 15:23:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/china-plays-key-role-climate-change-may-be-looked-additional-leadership-cop30-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>巴西食品加工机说2025年食品销售超出了期望</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/brazil-food-processor-says-2025-food-sales-exceed-expectations-2025-02-27/</link><description>高管周四表示，上市的肉类加工商BRF周四表示，食品销售超出了巴西的头两个月的预期，该公司计划扩大加工食品的生产，以从强劲的需求中获取收入。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 15:22:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/brazil-food-processor-says-2025-food-sales-exceed-expectations-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>洛根集团（Logan Group）从80％</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/logan-group-secures-backing-over-80-creditors-8-billion-debt-revamp-2025-02-27/</link><description>总部位于深圳的房地产开发商洛根集团（Logan Group）周四表示，已获得80.8％以上债权人的重组提案的支持，他们共同持有62.1亿美元的未偿还离岸债务。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 15:04:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/logan-group-secures-backing-over-80-creditors-8-billion-debt-revamp-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普誓言3月4日对加拿大墨西哥的关税，中国超过芬太尼的10％</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/trump-says-mexico-canada-tariffs-take-effect-march-4-2025-02-27/</link><description>美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）周四表示，他提议对墨西哥和加拿大商品的25％关税将于3月4日生效，同时对中国进口商品的额外关税，因为致命的毒品仍在从这些国家涌入美国。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 13:56:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/trump-says-mexico-canada-tariffs-take-effect-march-4-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国小米价格豪华电轿车比最初促进的低35％</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xiaomi-prices-luxury-electric-sedan-72932-2025-02-27/</link><description>中国的小米周四将其豪华电动轿车SU7 Ultra的初始标价降低了三分之一至529,900元（72,931.72美元），对世界上最大的汽车市场的特斯拉和波斯奇等人带来了更大的挑战。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 13:14:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xiaomi-prices-luxury-electric-sedan-72932-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普在4月1日之后决定所有国家的关税政策，哈塞特告诉CNBC</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-decide-tariff-policies-after-april-1-hassett-tells-cnbc-2025-02-27/</link><description>白宫经济顾问凯文·哈塞特（Kevin Hassett）在周四的一次采访中告诉CNBC，美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）将在4月1日进行研究后，将对包括墨西哥和加拿大在内的所有国家做出关税政策。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 13:03:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-decide-tariff-policies-after-april-1-hassett-tells-cnbc-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>随着贸易战的升级，经济学家押注中国的韧性</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/trade-war-escalates-economists-bet-china-resilience-2025-02-27/</link><description>随着中国处于美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税议程的最前沿，国内经济学家预计，随着贸易战的加剧，政策措施，供应链调整和加强全球合作伙伴关系的结合，加强了全球第二大经济体。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 12:19:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/trade-war-escalates-economists-bet-china-resilience-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>小米推出了15个超旗舰智能手机，价格为894美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/xiaomi-launches-15-ultra-flagship-smartphone-priced-894-2025-02-27/</link><description>世界第三大智能手机制造商小米（小米）在周四推出了新的旗舰智能手机小米15 Ultra，基本型号的起价为6,499元（894.19美元）。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 12:06:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/xiaomi-launches-15-ultra-flagship-smartphone-priced-894-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>医疗保健专家敦促印度重写临床试验规则，以提高全球市场份额</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/healthcare-experts-urge-india-rewrite-clinical-trial-rules-boost-global-market-2025-02-27/</link><description>医疗保健专家在一次行业会议上说，印度应该从中国和澳大利亚等国家的剧本中获取一页。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 11:43:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/healthcare-experts-urge-india-rewrite-clinical-trial-rules-boost-global-market-2025-02-27/</guid></item></channel></rss>